  "title": "Project Manager (M&E) - Jurong East",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a highly motivated and experienced <strong>Construction Project Manager (ACMV, M&amp;E)</strong> to lead and manage projects involving <strong>Air-Conditioning &amp; Mechanical Ventilation (ACMV)</strong> and <strong>Cold Room Systems</strong>. The ideal candidate will oversee all aspects of project execution — from planning and design to completion — ensuring quality, safety, and client satisfaction.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead and oversee projects related to <strong>ACMV and Cold Room Systems</strong>, ensuring timely and successful execution.</li>\n  <li>Possess sound knowledge in the <strong>design of air-conditioning &amp; mechanical ventilation systems</strong>, <strong>refrigeration systems</strong>, and <strong>cold room systems</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams, clients, and contractors to achieve project goals within established timelines and budgets.</li>\n  <li>Develop and manage <strong>project plans, schedules, and budgets</strong>, monitoring progress against key milestones.</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular <strong>site inspections</strong> to ensure compliance with <strong>quality standards</strong> and <strong>safety regulations</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Provide effective <strong>leadership and guidance</strong> to project teams, fostering a collaborative, high-performance environment.</li>\n  <li>Proactively address and resolve project-related challenges while maintaining open communication with stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Perform <strong>risk management</strong> to minimize potential project risks.</li>\n  <li>Interact and liaise with clients on a daily basis to ensure expectations are met.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Qualifications:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum <strong>Diploma in Engineering</strong> or related discipline.</li>\n  <li>Relevant <strong>work experience within the construction industry</strong> or a similar field.</li>\n  <li>Strong <strong>leadership</strong>, <strong>communication</strong>, and <strong>time management</strong> skills, with the ability to manage multiple projects concurrently.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in <strong>project management tools and software</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Possess a valid <strong>Singapore Class 3 Driving License</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Opportunity to lead exciting and impactful engineering projects.</li>\n  <li>Collaborative work culture and career development opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Competitive remuneration and benefits.</li>\n</ul>",
